#

Pina Colada

5 min
$5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Coconut

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Caribbean

Course:

Drink

Tags:

DrinkTropicalCocktail

Description

A refreshing tropical drink that blends sweet pineapple with creamy coconut.

Ingredients

  • pineapple juice: 1 cup
  • coconut cream: 1/2 cup
  • white rum: 1/2 cup
  • ice: 2 cups
  • pineapple slice (for garnish): 1 slice
  • maraschino cherry (for garnish): 1 cherry
